## Root Cause
| Attempt | Flag | Result |
|---|---|---|
| Without key | `--no-remote-rules` | Needs local rules, none provided |
| With Workbench key | `SCANOSS_API_KEY` | Key valid for SBOM API, not crypto-finder ruleset API |

## Fix Options
- **Option A:** Request crypto-finder API key → https://www.scanoss.com/try-it-now
- **Option B:** Use local YAML rules with `--no-remote-rules --rules-dir /workspace/rules`


